Level 1: The Beginning
You are Doctor Woo. The BARDIS, your space-time machine, is malfunctioning.  Can you leave the surreal planet on which you have landed and resume your travels?

You are standing on a green hill overlooking a village. Your BARDIS is parked rather incongruously next to a small group of trees. A muddy track leads south, and a narrow trail goes northwest
 into a thick mist
.

You can see the BARDIS.
You can go south, northwest or in.
> x me

> x me
Looking good, wearing a broad smile!

You are Doctor Woo, a traveller in space and time. Your height varies with incarnations but you're about 'average' at the moment. As an alien, you are immune to earthly diseases. You are also ambidextrous.

You are currently in 'Level 1: The Beginning'.
