> x car

> x car
The car is a nifty little runabout which has been driving northwards and has clearly broken down.
The front nearside tyre is flat and this probably explains why Mrs Hatch looks so upset.
 In the back seat there appears to be some kind of cylindrical object, which you can't make out. There is a sticker in the rear window.
 The boot is closed.
> open boot

> open boot
You open the boot.
Inside there is a car jack and a magazine.
> take car jack

> take car jack
You pick it up.
> read magazine

> read magazine
As you open the magazine, a contract drops out.

On reading the magazine you find an interesting article entitled "How Glass Objects Can Act as a Lens."
> take contract

> take contract
You pick it up.
> use car jack on car

> use car jack on car
You use the jack to raise up the car and this gives you the chance to free the wheel with a punctured tyre.  You pull it off and lay it on the ground pleased with your work.
