"Ah, I remember the days when Dr Whatsgone and I helped solve crimes and humiliate the whole of Scotland Yard," says Sherlock.  "But I seem to have lost heart in that and instead just stop the riff-raff from vandalising the graveyard.  The damn yobs, they stole my cane, you know..."
> ask sherlock bones about matches

> ask sherlock bones about matches
