According to a plaque on the gates, you are outside Fort Knots. It is a quietly foreboding citadel.

You can also see Monty Python.
You can go south or north.
> speak to monty python

> speak to monty python
"I am Monty Python," says the man, which was obvious given the name emblazoned on his uniform.  He strides around you in a strange half goose-stepping manner complete with strange wiggling of the hips before he speaks again.  "Ah strange visitor, I guess you wish to come inside to steal something, but I cannot permit you entry.  Since my quest for the Holy Nail ended in failure, my penace has been to stand here on guard."  He then blows you a raspberry!
> give jar to monty python

> give jar to monty python
You hand over the jar to Monty Python and he flexes, not hesitating to show his fearsome muscles.  With barely a flick of his wrist, the lid turns and the jar is opened. "Easy" he says, as he returns it to you.
