> give band aid dressing to rob geldof
You give the dressing to Rob, who puts in on his finger. He thanks you. "If some of that gas got in that wound I could have been really ill.  So, thanks for your kindness. Tell you what; have a look in my van and help yourself to anything that might prove useful."  He walks over to his van and opens the rear doors. A rat trap catches your eye.
> give large piece of cheese to rob geldof

> give large piece of cheese to rob geldof
You hand Rob the cheese and he fixes it into the rat trap. "There you are.  That should solve your rat problem."
