"You are the one who took a picture of my girl!" He isn't happy with you and smashes the camera.

"I'm sorry," you explain. "I thought I was doing Mr Camwrong a favour, but instead of helping me he wants a picture of you as well."

"Ah, he tricks lots of people so I have been told."  He nods sadly.  "Tell you what, if you get the picture back off Camwrong, I'll do you a favour in return.  We shall enact a blood oath to seal our promise."

He takes a knife and cuts his palm then yours.  You shake hands sealing your bond.
