Teleport Stop X: Secret Nuclear Bunker

You are in a secret nuclear bunker set up for times of international emergency.  There is a large computer console here which seems to control some kind of weaponry.
As you materialise, you crash into Mrs Seadock, whose hand was hovering over the red button on the computer console.

You can see a computer console, a DEFCON notice, Kojak and Mrs Seadock.
