The teleporter display says "You are Already There."
> speak to mrs seadock

> speak to mrs seadock
You think that Mrs Seadock has been knocked unconscious but when you get close she jumps up and disappears through a secret door. You follow her with Kojak...

...after a few minutes of frantic running, you emerge in Little Italy to find Mrs Seadock held in one of tiny Tom's famous wrestling holds. Kojak arrests her immediately.

You can also see Tom Crews (wearing sunglasses), Mrs Seadock and Kojak.
You can go east.
> speak to kojak

> speak to kojak
"Well done everyone," says Kojak. "I've checked with Tom, who has checked with his spiritual adviser, and it looks as if the full reward is going to you Woo." He hands you $100.

"We will be sweeping the area for the murder weapon," continues Kojak. "It should turn up soon."

He also finally realises that you have his notebook, so you hand it back.

You hear a ping from the newspaper suggesting something new has just arrived.
> speak to mrs seadock

> speak to mrs seadock
You ask Mrs Seadock for an explanation and immediately regret it. She takes a deep breath and launches into a long philosophical diatribe about what is wrong with this planet and how oblivion was the only solution. After a few minutes, and noticing Kojak glancing at his watch, you break in with "Thank you, that is all we need to know."

With that, Kojak walks Mrs Seadock off to the station, and you take a moment to enjoy your success.
